<![CDATA[<p class="MsoNormal" style=""><font face="arial">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Thank you for contacting Kingsbridge.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Please accept this email as confirmation that </span><b style="font-size: 12pt;">a card payment of £000.00 has been processed today to settle the outstanding balance</b><span style="font-size: 12pt;"> of your Close Brothers Premium Finance account.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br><i>(Delete as required) </i></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">I have sent a request to Close Brothers to cancel your Direct Debit agreement and they will write to you with confirmation of this.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>If you have any questions then please do not hesitate to contact us.<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>Kind regards,<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Accounts Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E: customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></p>]]></td>
